Some projects

  • Unfollower

    "Unfollower" is an application that allows you to unfollow in large numbers with a single click, and much more.

    Vue 2, Vuetify, Vercel, Instagram-private-api.

  • Basualdo

    "Basualdo" is a complete ecommerce with cart, checkout, and all the necessary features.

    Vue 2, Vuetify, Vuex, Pathify, Mercadopago, Express.

  • Vacaciones con cody

    "Vacaciones con cody" is a simple page designed for a code challenge from codigofacilito.com

    Html, Css, JS, Swiper.js, Github pages.

  • Cticial CSS Extractor

    "Cticial CSS Extractor" is a script that allows you to obtain the critical css of a website by using the chrome dev tools (with scraping).

    Node.js, Playwright.
